</taxonomicName>
is one of the species within the genus, with 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075EFFC51155061FFD79AB0B" baseAuthorityName="Feldmann &amp; Haggart" baseAuthorityYear="2007" box="[619,737,1044,1071]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="38" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="walkerae">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075EFFC51155061FFD79AB0B" box="[619,737,1044,1071]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="61">S. walkerae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, to exhibit an inflated gastro-orbital lobe. Its thin ornamentation is also distinct from that of 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075EFFC5129C065EFD97AB4B" baseAuthorityName="Secretan" baseAuthorityYear="1964" box="[418,527,1108,1134]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="38" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="australis">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075EFFC5129C065EFD97AB4B" box="[418,527,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="61">S. australis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075EFFC51125065EFD3DAB4B" baseAuthorityName="Secretan" baseAuthorityYear="1964" box="[539,677,1108,1134]" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="38" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="granulifera">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075EFFC51125065EFD3DAB4B" box="[539,677,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="61">S. granulifera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="66DC4D1C075EFFC5118F065EFF24ABAB" baseAuthorityName="Hyzny, Schlogl, Charbonnier, Schweigert, Rulleau &amp; Gouttenoire" baseAuthorityYear="2015" class="Malacostraca" family="Erymidae" genus="Stenodactylina" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="38" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lagardettei">
<emphasis id="93A8EA8D075EFFC5118F065EFF24ABAB" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="61">S. lagardettei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
